section#description-step(ng-form='descriptionStepForm')
  .page-header
    h1.text-center Step Two: Tell Us About Yourself
  .alert.alert-info
    p#search-info-message Describe who you are and what you're looking for. Don't worry about price and other desired amenities - that comes later.
      a(href='#') Read more.
  .form-group
    label.col-md-2.col-md-offset-2.control-label(for='input-description') Description
    .col-md-5
      textarea#txt-description.form-control(placeholder='Hi, my name is Amy! I'm looking for a place within walking distance of...', ng-model='search.search_attrs.description', required='required')
      span.help-block
        | A longer block of help text that breaks onto a new line and may extend beyond one line.
